                Know how your brand shows up in <span class="text-blue-600">AI Search.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Consumers are moving from Google to LLMs. Ranklore helps you monitor, protect, and optimize your brand’s "lore" across the AI landscape.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-12 relative max-w-2xl mx-auto">
